  "description": "A striking close-up photograph showcases a butterfly perched atop a textured, brown surface. The butterfly's wings are its most prominent feature, displaying a captivating combination of deep blue, orange, and black patterns. The upper wing showcases a gradient of blue hues accented with vibrant orange spots, while the lower wing exhibits a more subdued grey-black coloration with smaller orange and white spots. The butterfly's body is black with subtle iridescent highlights.  Its antennae are thin and delicate, extending upwards. The background is blurred, focusing attention on the butterfly and the rough, organic texture of the surface it rests upon.",
